      <title>巴里克可能因与政府的争端而关闭马里矿场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴里克黄金公司表示，马里军政府已经阻止了该国最大金矿的货运，如果货运继续暂停，该公司将需要停止该矿的作业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/barrick-may-close-mali-gold-mine-over-dispute-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可价格创下新高，给巧克力制造商和消费者带来沉重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/cocoa-soars-to-fresh-record-in-blow-to-world-s-chocolate-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场努力应对新一轮的供应担忧，纽约可可期货价格创下新高，这增加了已经困扰巧克力制造商和消费者的高成本进一步恶化的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/cocoa-soars-to-fresh-record-in-blow-to-world-s-chocolate-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Elliott 拆分计划后，霍尼韦尔考虑拆分航空航天业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/honeywell-weighs-aerospace-split-after-elliott-s-breakup-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[霍尼韦尔国际公司 (Honeywell International Inc.) 表示，正在考虑战略选择，包括可能剥离其航空航天业务。一个月前，埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 曾呼吁拆分这家工业集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/honeywell-weighs-aerospace-split-after-elliott-s-breakup-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 11:46:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦将利率降至两年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/pakistan-cuts-interest-rates-to-spur-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦将基准利率下调至两年多以来的最低水平，因为通胀的缓解为央行促进经济增长提供了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/pakistan-cuts-interest-rates-to-spur-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 11:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
