    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德在丹麦投资 12 亿美元建新工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/novo-nordisk-invests-1-2-billion-in-new-factory-in-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ozempic 生产商诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 为满足其重磅药物的需求采取了两大步，在获得以 117 亿美元收购海外三家大型工厂的批准后不久，该公司又承诺斥资 85 亿丹麦克朗（12 亿美元）在丹麦建造一家新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/novo-nordisk-invests-1-2-billion-in-new-factory-in-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因中国数据疲软削弱需求前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国公布的一系列经济数据加剧了人们对这一最大进口国需求减弱的担忧，油价在上周上涨后下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决议前乐观情绪推动美国股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周晚些时候，全球各大央行将公布利率决定，交易员们对此十分关注，美国股市因此上涨。比特币价格创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析人士称，萨赫勒军政府不太可能逆转退出贸易集团的进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/west-african-juntas-given-six-months-to-rethink-trade-bloc-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非领导人给予马里、尼日尔和布基纳法索六个月的时间重新考虑退出该地区经济集团，作为避免该集团分裂的最后一次努力。]]></description>
